Class UpdateBlockStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tenforce.semtech.SPARQLParser.SPARQLStatements.BlockStatement
      • com.tenforce.semtech.SPARQLParser.SPARQLStatements.UpdateBlockStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStatement

    public class UpdateBlockStatement
extends BlockStatement
    A SPARQL Update block is defined as: - it starts with a '{' - it ends with a '}' - it may contain statements (which are just stored as Strings) - it may contain innerblocks, those inner blocks look like: - GRAPH { [this is a new block] }
